1) cd fluffos-2*
2) ./configure lpuni
3) make
4) make install
5) cd ../bin
6) vi config.lpuni

change the following entries:

name
mudlib directory
binary directory

7) ./driver ./config.lpuni &
8) telnet localhost 1336


Enjoy!

If you run into trouble, feel free to post on the LPUni
section of http://lpmuds.net/forum


